<\body>
  <doc-data|<doc-title|The Jacobi Polynomials>>

  <\equation>
    P<rsub|n><rsup|><around|(|x|)>=<choice|<tformat|<table|<row|<cell|n=0>|<cell|1>>|<row|<cell|n=1>|<cell|<frac|\<alpha\>-\<beta\>+x<around*|(|2+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>|)>|2>>>|<row|<cell|n=2>|<cell|A<rsub|n>*x*P<rsub|n-1><rsup|><around|(|x|)>-B<rsub|n>*P<rsub|n-2><rsup|><around|(|x|)>>>>>>
  </equation>

  Where:

  <\equation>
    <tabular|<tformat|<table|<row|<cell|A<rsub|n>>|<cell|=<frac|<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>-1|)>*<around|(|a<rsup|2>-b<rsup|2>+<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>-2|)>*<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>|)>|)>|2*n*<around|(|n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>|)>*<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>-2|)>>>>|<row|<cell|>|<cell|=<frac|<around|(|C<rsub|n>-1|)>*<around|(|\<alpha\><rsup|2>-\<beta\><rsup|2>+C<rsub|n-1>*C<rsub|n>|)>|2*n*C<rsub|<frac|n|2>>*C<rsub|n-1>>>>|<row|<cell|>|<cell|>>|<row|<cell|B<rsub|n>>|<cell|=<frac|<around|(|n+\<alpha\>-1|)>*<around|(|n+\<beta\>-1|)>*<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>|)>|n*<around|(|n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>|)>*<around|(|2*n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>-2|)>>>>|<row|<cell|>|<cell|=<frac|<around|(|n+\<alpha\>-1|)>*<around|(|n+\<beta\>-1|)>*C<rsub|n>|n*C<rsub|<frac|n|2>>
    C<rsub|n-1>>>>|<row|<cell|>|<cell|>>|<row|<cell|C<rsub|n>>|<cell|=2n+\<alpha\>+\<beta\>>>>>>
